snippet.title: Revisiting Gabby Petito: Brian Entin and Jennifer Coffindaffer rethink old clues | Banfield
snippet.description:
The City of North Port, Florida unveiled a memorial bench in Gabby's honor on November 22. The bench is covered in steel butterflies, a favorite of Gabby's.

Former FBI agent Jennifer Coffindaffer joins Brian Entin to revisit the case of Gabby Petito and determine what, if anything, the authorities may have missed.

Watch Ashleigh Banfield's Talk Show on NewsNation weeknights at 10/9c.
